# 创建 scater 要求的对象
sce <- SingleCellExperiment(
  assays = list(counts = as.matrix(counts)), 
  colData = meta
)

exprs(sce) <- log2(
  calculateCPM(sce ) + 1)

运行 tSNE 降维算法

!!!!!!!!! the bigger perplexity is, the more neighborhood number is.

set.seed(1000)
sce <- runTSNE(sce, perplexity=10)
plotTSNE(sce, 
         shape_by= "plate", 
         colour_by= "g")

对tSNE降维后结果进行不同的聚类

!!!!!! Note: PCA, UMAP, tSNE are dimensional reduction methods. kmeans and hcluster are cluster methods

colData(sce)$tSNE_kmeans <- as.character(kmeans(sce@int_colData@listData$reducedDims$TSNE,
                                                centers = 4)$clust)

hc=hclust(dist(sce@int_colData@listData$reducedDims$TSNE ))
plot(hc)

clus = cutree(hc, 4) 
colData(sce)$tSNE_hc <-  as.character(clus)
plotTSNE(sce,  colour_by = "tSNE_kmeans")

plotTSNE(sce,  colour_by = "tSNE_hc")

table(colData(sce)$tSNE_hc , colData(sce)$tSNE_kmeans)

SC3 package with scater

library(SC3) # BiocManager::install(‘SC3’) sce <- sc3_estimate_k(sce1) ## evaluate how many number of cluster metadata(sce)\(sc3\)k_estimation ## preprocess before sc3 command rowData(sce)$feature_symbol=rownames(rowData(sce)) # 耗费时间 kn=4 sc3_cluster=“sc3_4_clusters” # 非常耗时 sce <- sc3(sce, ks = kn, biology = TRUE)

sc3_plot_consensus(sce, k = kn, show_pdata = c(sc3_cluster)) sc3_plot_expression(sce, k = kn, show_pdata = c(sc3_cluster)) sc3_plot_markers(sce, k = kn, show_pdata = c(sc3_cluster)) plotPCA(sce, shape_by= “g” , colour_by = sc3_cluster ) sc3_interactive(sce)
